		{
			description: ["Welcome to Craft to Exile 2. Open your Master Bag and take stock of what you carry. This world is governed by intertwined forces — industrial machinery and magical power, tested by an ARPG combat layer that scales every fight. Your journey begins here, on the ground, with nothing but your talent and your will."]
