			dependencies: ["73CE4DB9AE29B81C"]
			description: ["Wood is the universal starting material. Collect enough logs to begin crafting Tinkers' Construct pattern blanks — the templates used to shape tool parts. Your first tools will be made from wood and stone, but the materials system that follows will take you far beyond vanilla crafting."]
