			dependencies: ["1319819B00FEA874"]
			description: ["Your first Tinkers' tool should be a stone pickaxe head on a wood handle — functional but temporary. Upgrade to iron parts as soon as possible. Each material carries unique traits: iron is durable and straightforward, while exotic materials found later offer passive abilities that fundamentally change how tools perform. Read 'Materials and You' for the full breakdown."]
